<title>Select Relative or Absolute Positioning</title>

To toggle between <link relative_and_absolute_mode.hgt>Relative and Absolute</link> positioning, select <b>Options</b> from the <link data_dictionary_menu.hgt>menu bar</link>, then select <b>Relative Positions</b>. A checkmark indicates your file is in <b>Relative Positioning</b>; the absence of a checkmark indicates the file is using <b>Absolute Positioning</b>.
